These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, soy-milk, juice
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, traveling, singing, magic-tricks
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, accountant, librarian, writer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, crime, animation
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, indie, dubstep, funk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: vaning, rowing, cycling, surfing
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bus, ship, van
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching scientific movies##1
 2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
 4. the accountant is on the far right##1
 5. the accountant is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is the person drinking 7up##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the librarian##1
 8. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person driving the van is the fan of indie##1
10. the person driving the bus is on the right of the coach##1
11. the person who's sport is vaning is the person drinking 7up##1
12. the person driving the bus is the fan of dubstep##1
13. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
14. the person who's sport is rowing is the person drinking juice##1
15. the person who's sport is surfing is the librarian##1
16. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the coach##1
17. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate       | juice      | soy-milk       | 7up    |
| Hobby         | reading    | magic-tricks    | traveling      | singing    |
| Job           | writer | coach       | librarian | accountant     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific         | crime  | animation      | romance     |
| Music-Genre   | indie          | funk     | dubstep       | metal |
| Sport         | cycling       | rowing | surfing       | vaning   |
| Transport     | van     | ship  | bus         | motorbike   |

