.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, artichoke, spinach, kale
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, video-games, puzzles, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, romance, disaster, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, country, metal, reggae
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, colombian, malaysian, american
4 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, mouse, pony
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, snowmobile, helicopter
 1. the person eating kale is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the colombian is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 3. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 4. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the fan of reggae is the person watching romance movies##1
 6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the fan of gospel is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 8. the person watching disaster movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the indian is on the left of the american##1
10. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
11. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
12. the american is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
13. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
14. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
15. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1
16. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
17. the american is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3      |      4      |
| Food          | spinach     | artichoke     | asparagus      | kale  |
| Hobby         | woodworking  | camping  | puzzles      | video-games |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | disaster     | scientific | romance        |
| Music-Genre   | gospel    | country        | metal        | reggae        |
| Nationality   | malaysian | indian | american   | colombian  |
| Pet           | pony   | goat       | hedgehog        | mouse       |
| Transport     | scooter     | snowmobile     | helicopter       | taxi     |

