.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cherry, peach, tomato, pepper
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, filmmaking, skydiving, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, doctor, paramedic, lawyer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, spy, zombie, action
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, hip-hop, salsa, house
4 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, ferret, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, baseball, volleyball, snowboarding
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 2. the person eating peach is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 3. the fan of metal is the person eating peach##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the lawyer is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 8. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the mouse is the person watching spy movies##1
11. the doctor is the person eating cherry##1
12. the person eating pepper is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
13. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
14. the paramedic is on the far left##1
15. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the fan of house##1
16. the lawyer is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
17. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | tomato          | pepper        | peach      | cherry      |
| Hobby         | chess       | skydiving       | photography    | filmmaking |
| Job           | paramedic        | scientist     | lawyer | doctor        |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | action   | spy      | thriller      |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop         | salsa          | metal       | house      |
| Pet           | rabbit    | pony           | mouse       | ferret      |
| Sport         | baseball | snowboarding | volleyball   | golf      |

